        "name": "Ritual Nails",
        "description": "Locke readies a set of Soul Nails to throw, dealing damage to and marking enemies hit. Locke can consume the marks to deal bonus damage with his attacks.",
        "tooltip": "Locke readies a set of <keywordMajor>Soul Nails</keywordMajor> to throw, dealing <magicDamage>{{ missiledamage }} magic damage</magicDamage> and marking enemies hit. Nails apply a {{ slowamount1*100 }}/{{ slowamount2*100 }}/{{ slowamount3*100 }}% <status>Slow</status> for {{ slowduration1 }}/{{ slowduration2 }}/{{ slowduration3 }} seconds, stacking with the amount of nails hit.<br /><br />Attacking the enemy consumes the <keywordMajor>Soul Nails</keywordMajor>, dealing <magicDamage>{{ naildamage }} magic damage</magicDamage> per stack, increased by {{ twomarkbonuspercent }}% and {{ threemarkbonuspercent }}% for two and three nails respectively.{{ spellmodifierdescriptionappend }}",
